flowchart LR
    %% Actors/Entities
    U["fa:fa-user User Account"]
    Admin["fa:fa-user-cog Admin (Instance of User)"]

    %% System components
    C["fa:fa-users Channel"]

    %% Admin actions (tied to the channel)
    AdminAction1["fa:fa-plus-circle Create Protected Channel"]
    AdminAction2["fa:fa-users Assign Roles in Channel"]
    AdminAction3["fa:fa-tasks Assign Tasks"]
    AdminAction4["fa:fa-check Close Task"]
    AdminAction5["fa:fa-tools Manage Channels"]
    AdminAction6["fa:fa-link Generate and Send Invite Link"]

    %% Actions performed within the channel
    ChannelAction1["fa:fa-envelope Send Message"]
    ChannelAction2["fa:fa-file-upload Upload File"]
    ChannelAction3["fa:fa-tasks Manage Tasks"]
    ChannelAction4["fa:fa-edit Edit Message"]
    ChannelAction5["fa:fa-poll-h Create Poll"]
    ChannelAction6["fa:fa-comment-alt Private Chat"]
    ChannelAction7["fa:fa-bell Manage Notification Settings"]
    ChannelAction8["fa:fa-search Search in Channel"]

    %% Relationships between entities and actions
    U --> |Uses| C
    C --> |Allows| ChannelAction1 & ChannelAction2 & ChannelAction3 & ChannelAction4 & ChannelAction5 & ChannelAction6 & ChannelAction7 & ChannelAction8

    %% Admin uses, creates, and manages the channel
    Admin --> |Uses, Creates, Manages| C
    Admin --> AdminAction1 & AdminAction2 & AdminAction3 & AdminAction4 & AdminAction5 & AdminAction6
    C --> |Admin Manages| AdminAction1 & AdminAction2 & AdminAction3 & AdminAction4 & AdminAction5 & AdminAction6

    %% Admin manages users and their privileges
    Admin --> |Manages & Grants Privileges to| U
